data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. **Motivated seller offering the buyer's a choice- 10K off list price or 10K seller contributions towards buyer's closing costs or rate buy down with full price offer** Are you a first time home buyer or looking to downsize? Don't let this one get away! Charming 3 bed, 2 bath one story home in a popular SE Salem neighborhood. Newer furnace, roof, water heater and barrier in crawl space. Room for RV parking with 30 amp hookups on side of the home. Washer, dryer and hot tub stay with the home.
